quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  21,58,phir un ko toar kar rezah rezah kardiya magar aik barray ( buut ) ko ( nah tora ) taakay woh is ki taraf rujoo karen
  21,59,kehnay lagey ke hamaray mabodon ke sath yeh maamla kis nekiya? woh to koi zalim hai
  21,60,logon ne kaha ke hum ne aik jawan ko un ka zikar karte hue suna hai is ko ibrahim kehte hain
  21,61,woh bolay ke usay logon ke samnay lao taakay gawah rahen
  21,62,( jab ibrahim aeye to ) buut paraston ne kaha ke ibrahim bhala yeh kaam hamaray mabodon ke sath tum nekiya hai ?
  21,63,( ibrahim ne ) kaha ( nahi ) balkay yeh un ke is barray ( buut ) nekiya ( hoga ). agar yeh boltay hain to un se pooch lau
  21,64,unhon ne apne dil ghhorkiya to aapas mein kehnay lagey be shak tum hi be insaaf ho
  21,65,phir ( sharminda ho kar ) sir neecha karliya ( is par bhi ibrahim se kehnay lagey ke ) tum jantay ho yeh boltay nahi
  21,66,( ibrahim ne ) kaha phir tum khuda ko chore kar kyun aisi cheezon ko pujte ho jo nah tumhe kuch faida day saken aur nuqsaan pouncha saken ?
  21,67,taf hai tum par aur jin ko tum khuda ke siwa pujte ho un par bhikiya tum aqal nahi rakhtay ?
  21,68,( tab woh ) kehnay lagey ke agar tumhe ( is se apne mabood ka intiqam lena aur ) kuch karna hai to is ko jala do aur apne mabodon ki madad karo
  21,69,hum ne hukum diya ae aag sard hoja aur ibrahim par ( mojab ) salamti ( ban ja )
  21,70,aur un logon ne bura to un ka chaha tha magar hum ne un hi ko nuqsaan mein daal diya
  21,71,aur ibrahim aur Loot ko is sarzamen ki taraf bacha nikala jis mein hum ne ahal aalam ke liye barket rakhi thi
  21,72,aur hum ne ibrahim ko ashq ataa kiye. aur mstzad bar-aan Yaqoob . aur sab ko naik bakhtkiya
